                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A gaki takes 1d4 points of fire damage every round it\u2019s exposed to the light of a full moon. It takes 1d4 points of cold damage every round it is exposed to direct sunlight."
